[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering javap features**\n\nI'm thinking about how the `javap` tool can display line numbers around methods in Java code. It's an interesting feature that would likely help developers trace and debug their code more effectively. I wonder if this capability is widely known or utilized in typical workflows. It seems like a handy aspect to use for understanding the structure of a class file and its methods, especially when debugging. Perhaps I should explore this in more detail!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0c1f276e256b026b0169f4e47c7528819db4c4e9c46704868f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9OR-38RlE87dAyfBFmb9A9aBaoJLUOp1kEWbPf5idFEQpqu2fLZwbSZYVRr7vvchF_KKdrMHmdyYm_0Gy1HAF-RSjpthjLue07SZoggaBf21a3pBu4kbVWe5seh2r08wcU4uGXhjHZ3df2_jS4nbmrONIhpo21eYzUPQdc5jYKDzHZpI8hvgQaTuKdqWpmbTPH8Ujv6vKXmApEsFmLIoAkMM59Xyy02oeMRXbbCmYKqeUSjC3j1UJLxLrMK7GKI_UtQEy_NEBMZnnFs2PG6c1s9xj37mQaH5UgbUsbQr1pEz69zszTu4PeznQqrCqf9FyqDhCSuDXjSZWUN0L_sKJIiYtbSNbg33MajhN8TVgN0R9Jtfi3Zixagf0NzGHHdgTr_2o8_IUDEL9Oppk1w96PeEjqXSvQ_XoQduWVXbJuZBl6j0AZMKaQDpL1jWZjndKPVlqtbKNn9pM9i6orw9VTQh4pYR_54Xl_-K_FzBVVLJXogZQ0epG51qDw1BmulCUk01p_o1WmuWrNnFMS11gJN4-MEEHQjR4kscMLjJOZaBmZlrz9Zo8FySJheURiX8rMNHkfpqBBKztmD2PVAAJ37ruQ4kF-nBRweUQzYn0HKqLgz46tQWBG14e7rigjBGDvrn-szGemZsweIL3_zwgA0Rf28P4PqFI-UO303K4g2q0neu2JjZTPJdSOqsYzytbY8PHAyvYkYduDftuu5S_bFZ90B-uKMDU5TGEfKkzbajboG-qdhvXyc2dKyPo0DL73uaVbaB4NVnb3Cyh3u_n5WiaXVwzqfWyU-kBgRmh2iRsaQ-be7O7Sw6BKwf972IIVT1hbitRl20NwGW5tVZb439xV9z5ytrASE6ZQCLScpfHPSw-dM5XNKWTH75n0pMfXLfqhPaZZRUPNQGV67nk98Kbt9vTGfiMi4LVa8A5og85T96470F3XDJvCsmOQR527I-Hm8qEyO4AG8cXkw-BON7n8UTFILJQ8qHa_W1b0Wawjw=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering javap features**\\n\\nI'm thinking about how the `javap` tool can display line numbers around methods in Java code. It's an interesting feature that would likely help developers trac